             line="243">Sets a #GflsUnsavedDocumentTitleCallback function. To reset to the default
setting, pass %NULL to @title_callback.

The callback will be used by gfls_unsaved_document_titles_get_title().

Examples:
- "Unsaved Document N"
- "Unsaved File N"
- "Untitled Document N"
- "New Document N"
- Etc.</doc>
